82
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:32,620
But I don't want this event to go wrong.

83
00:04:32,620 --> 00:04:38,620
Before I become vice chairman, I want to prove my strength at this event.

84
00:04:38,620 --> 00:04:41,700
Khun Sasa, you're going to be the vice chairman.

85
00:04:41,700 --> 00:04:43,260
What about Khun Sira?

86
00:04:43,260 --> 00:04:44,858
He'll be the chairman.

87
