89
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:57,000
- I think...
- Brother, don't think too much.

90
00:04:57,000 --> 00:05:01,980
I said that because I wanted the word to get to Grandma.

91
00:05:01,980 --> 00:05:04,200
So, Grandma will trust me.

92
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:10,080
Do you think Grandma would be comfortable letting Kheetika follow you?

93
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:11,460
I know.

94
00:05:11,460 --> 00:05:13,120
But if I don't do that,

95
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:17,860
Kheetika and I won't go back to the old days.

96
00:05:17,860 --> 00:05:21,540
I don't think you should think about Kheetika and you.

97
00:05:21,540 --> 00:05:23,820
Let's see how the chairwoman reacts.

98
00:05:23,820 --> 00:05:26,460
See if she believes what you're doing.

99
00:05:26,460 --> 00:05:28,520
I can't wait any longer, Brother.

100
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:31,720
