185
00:12:33,940 --> 00:12:37,180
- Didn't he ask her to help with his work?
- Work is work.

186
00:12:37,180 --> 00:12:40,580
It's not just Khun Sasa. Khun Sira is no different.

187
00:12:40,580 --> 00:12:42,640
He bought a ring for Khun Kheetika.

188
00:12:42,640 --> 00:12:44,300
Are you sure it's not fake news?

189
00:12:44,300 --> 00:12:46,100
I'm sure.

190
00:12:46,100 --> 00:12:49,540
