199
00:13:19,940 --> 00:13:21,180
Is it true?

200
00:13:21,180 --> 00:13:23,426
Do you want to keep talking?

201
00:13:23,426 --> 00:13:24,660
Sorry.

202
00:13:24,660 --> 00:13:27,927
It's all rumors. The rumors will fade soon.

203
00:13:27,927 --> 00:13:30,380
Rumors don't go away easily, Khun Sira.

204
00:13:30,380 --> 00:13:35,380
If this reaches the chairwoman, she won't let it go.

205
00:13:35,380 --> 00:13:39,580
Maybe she will fire Khun Kheetika.

206
00:13:52,100 --> 00:13:55,180
Excuse me! Excuse me, wait.

207
00:13:55,180 --> 00:13:59,420
Please let Nong Thatha go first. Thank you.

208
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:04,980
- Wow, she's beautiful.
- She's beautiful.

209
00:14:04,980 --> 00:14:06,620
