215
00:14:23,150 --> 00:14:24,960
Yes.

216
00:14:50,260 --> 00:14:51,860
What are you doing?

217
00:14:51,860 --> 00:14:54,220
Nothing.

218
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:57,860
