226
00:15:21,500 --> 00:15:25,140
I think you should invite Mr. Sasa to dinner. Because he's responsible for that project.

227
00:15:25,140 --> 00:15:27,560
Sasa wouldn't want to go with me.

228
00:15:27,560 --> 00:15:31,320
We often eat together. We're kind of bored with it. Right?

229
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:34,460
Is it okay, Khun Sira?

230
00:15:34,460 --> 00:15:37,360
You know what? What you said the other day

231
00:15:37,360 --> 00:15:40,160
enlightened me and made me want to change.

232
00:15:40,160 --> 00:15:43,760
Yes. If it weren't for Khun Sira,

233
00:15:43,760 --> 00:15:47,360
Thatha wouldn't be so hot.

234
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:50,620
It's okay.

235
00:15:50,620 --> 00:15:54,160
I have decided to attend dinner with you.

236
00:15:54,160 --> 00:15:56,360
However, I would like to bring Khun Kheetika with me.

237
00:15:56,360 --> 00:16:02,260
Because she has assisted me in enlightening you.

238
00:16:03,640 --> 00:16:05,400
Okay.

239
00:16:05,400 --> 00:16:07,720
Do I have to go?

240
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:20,340
The salmon here is delicious.

241
00:16:20,340 --> 00:16:23,480
Khun Sira. Have a taste.

242
00:16:28,380 --> 00:16:31,820
Khun Sira doesn't eat raw food.

243
00:16:43,100 --> 00:16:47,440
This one. The roast beef here is also delicious.

244
00:16:50,540 --> 00:16:52,600
I don't eat beef.

245
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:57,280
I'll take it.

